      <div class="hero-card-title">What we’ll ask you about</div>
      <ul class="hero-card-list">
        <li>
          <div class="hero-dot"></div>
          <div>
            Your current situation: household, work, or business constraints in California.
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <div class="hero-dot"></div>
